@@TJvCustomEdit.GroupIndex
Summary
  Allows edit controls to work together as a group.
Description
  When GroupIndex is set to -1, the edit control behaves as normal.
  
  Edit controls with the same GroupIndex property value (other than -1), work together as a group.
  When the user enters one of these edit controls, the text on the other edits belonging to the same
  group will be cleared.

